<view class="page">
  <view class="hero home-hero">
    <text class="hero-title">必火AI员工</text>
    <text class="hero-subtitle">手机上发消息，电脑端 online 执行，结果里的图片和视频可直接保存。</text>
    <view class="hero-actions">
      <button class="light-btn" bindtap="goMessages">进入消息</button>
      <button class="outline-light-btn" bindtap="goProfile">个人中心</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-head">
      <text class="section-title inline-title">账号状态</text>
      <view class="dot {{phoneBound ? 'ok' : 'warn'}}"></view>
    </view>
    <text class="status-text">{{statusText}}</text>
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="ghost-btn" bindtap="login">微信登录</button>
      <button class="primary-btn" open-type="getPhoneNumber" bindgetphonenumber="onGetPhoneNumber">授权手机号</button>
    </view>
    <text class="muted bind-tip">手机号用于匹配已经开通的 online 账号；未注册手机号不会创建 online 版本。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <text class="section-title">快捷消息</text>
    <view class="quick-grid">
      <button wx:for="{{quickMessages}}" wx:key="title" class="quick-card" data-index="{{index}}" bindtap="quickMessage">
        <text class="quick-title">{{item.title}}</text>
        <text class="quick-text">{{item.text}}</text>
      </button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section slim-section">
    <text class="section-title">检查手机号</text>
    <input class="input" type="number" maxlength="11" value="{{phoneInput}}" bindinput="onPhoneInput" placeholder="输入手机号，检查是否已有 online" />
    <view class="button-row">
      <button class="ghost-btn" bindtap="checkPhone">检查</button>
    </view>
    <text wx:if="{{phoneCheckText}}" class="muted check-result">{{phoneCheckText}}</text>
  </view>
</view>
